BT /F1 16 Tf 48 790 Td (README.md) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 766 Td (# E-commerce Chatbot) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 757 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 748 Td (A Python chatbot for a CoffeeMugs e-commerce store. It can answer product questions, show ) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 739 Td (available products, track orders, create orders, cancel orders, update delivery addresses, and ) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 730 Td (let an admin update order status.) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 721 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 712 Td (The project includes both a Tkinter GUI and a command-line chat interface.) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 703 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 694 Td (## Features) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 685 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 676 Td (- Intent classification with PyTorch) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 667 Td (- Product catalog lookup from `products.csv`) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 658 Td (- Content-based product recommendations using product attributes, browsing context, and ) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 649 Td (cart/order context) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 640 Td (- Product popularity analysis from saved database orders) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 631 Td (- Simple market basket analysis for frequently bought product pairs from saved database orders) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 622 Td (- Product category prediction using a small Naive Bayes ML model trained from `products.csv`) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 613 Td (- Order tracking and management through SQL Server) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 604 Td (- CSV seeding from `orders.csv`) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 595 Td (- GUI chat app with admin login support) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 586 Td (- CLI chat app for terminal use) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 577 Td (- Training script for rebuilding `data.pth` from `intents.json`) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 568 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 559 Td (## Requirements) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 550 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 541 Td (- Python 3.10 or newer) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 532 Td (- SQL Server) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 523 Td (- Microsoft ODBC Driver 18 for SQL Server) Tj ET
BT /F2 7 Tf 48 514 Td (- Python packages from `requirements.txt`) Tj ET
